%e A392461 a(6) = 9: The set {0, 1, 3, 5, 8, 9} has differences 1,2,2,3,1,3,4,5,4,5,7,6,8,8,9, with no difference appearing more than 2 times, so a(6)<=9. That a(6)>=9 requires exhaustive search.
